<p class=\"my-4 only:my-0 w-full\">Do you like tinkering in your garage? Are you fascinated by the wonders of science? Do you think innovation is the key to a better future? Then become an Axiom mechanic to be at the forefront of progress! In just 50 years, the Axiom Faction has completely transformed Asgartha and its people's way of life. Trams now circulate within the capital and aerodynes have brought all the Provinces within just a few hours' travel! Thanks to Kelon, your city lights up at night, and thanks to Constructs, Alteration is within everyone's grasp! All these marvels are the fruit of hard work performed by our engineers, workers and technicians. Through them, the industrial revolution is marching forward! Join us now!</p></div></div></div>",
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "quote",
        "text": "You can't choose when and where a quick fix will be needed."
      },
      {
        "type": "section",
        "title": "Story",
        "paragraphs": [
          "Do you like tinkering in your garage? Are you fascinated by the wonders of science? Do you think innovation is the key to a better future? Then become an Axiom mechanic to be at the forefront of progress! In just 50 years, the Axiom Faction has completely transformed Asgartha and its people's way of life. Trams now circulate within the capital and aerodynes have brought all the Provinces within just a few hours' travel! Thanks to Kelon, your city lights up at night, and thanks to Constructs, Alteration is within everyone's grasp! All these marvels are the fruit of hard work performed by our engineers, workers and technicians. Through them, the industrial revolution is marching forward! Join us now!"
        ]
